Package org.simreal.annotation

package org.simreal.annotation
  • Annotation Interfaces
    Class
    Description
    SimAgent
    The SimAgent annotation is used to mark types (classes or interfaces) that represent agents in a simulation model.
    SimChart
    The SimChart annotation is used to mark methods that generate or manipulate charts in a simulation model.
    SimDB
    The SimDB annotation is used to mark methods that are associated with a database table.
    SimField
    The SimField annotation is used to mark fields that are associated with a database table.
    SimModel
    The SimModel annotation is used to mark types (classes or interfaces) that are associated with a model.
    SimParam
    The SimParam annotation is used to mark parameters that are associated with a simulation model.
